### --- Search (GET /reservations/search) ---

###
### Search all reservations, paginated and sorted
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/search?page=0&size=2&sort=startDate,desc

###
### Search by id (also covers "get single reservation by id")
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/search?ids=1

###
### Search by multiple ids (IN)
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/search?ids=1&ids=2&ids=3

###
### Search by userId
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/search?userIds=1

###
### Search by multiple userIds (IN)
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/search?userIds=1&userIds=2

###
### Search by multiple userIds, comma-separated (equivalent to repeated params above)
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/search?userIds=1,2

###
### Search by roomId
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/search?roomIds=101

###
### Search by status
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/search?statuses=PENDING

###
### Search by exact startDate
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/search?startDate=2023-10-01

###
### Search by exact endDate
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/search?endDate=2023-10-05

###
### Search combined (AND across fields)
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/search?statuses=PENDING&roomIds=101

###
### Search combined, no match (expect empty page, still 200)
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/search?userIds=1&statuses=CANCELLED

###
### Search by nonexistent id (expect empty page, NOT 404 — /search always returns 200)
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/search?ids=999999

### --- Active in period (GET /reservations/active) ---

###
### Reservations active in a given period (overlap, excludes CANCELLED)
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/active?from=2023-10-01&to=2023-10-10

###
### Invalid: from > to (expect 400)
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/active?from=2026-10-20&to=2026-10-01

###
### Invalid: missing 'to' (expect 400)
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/active?from=2026-10-01

###
### Invalid: missing both params (expect 400)
GET http://localhost:8080/reservations/active

### --- Create (POST /reservations/create) ---

###
### Create reservation (id and status must be null)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 11,
  "roomId": 111,
  "startDate": "2026-07-01",
  "endDate": "2026-07-05"
}

### --- Update (PUT /reservations/update?id=) ---

###
### Update reservation (only PENDING can be updated)
PUT http://localhost:8080/reservations/update?id=11
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 11,
  "roomId": 1000,
  "startDate": "2026-07-01",
  "endDate": "2026-07-10"
}

###
### Invalid: missing 'id' param (expect 400)
PUT http://localhost:8080/reservations/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 11,
  "roomId": 1000,
  "startDate": "2026-07-01",
  "endDate": "2026-07-10"
}

###
### Invalid: reservation not found (expect 404)
PUT http://localhost:8080/reservations/update?id=999999
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 11,
  "roomId": 1000,
  "startDate": "2026-07-01",
  "endDate": "2026-07-10"
}

### --- Delete (DELETE /reservations/delete?id=) ---

###
### Delete reservation
DELETE http://localhost:8080/reservations/delete?id=1

###
### Invalid: missing 'id' param (expect 400)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/reservations/delete

###
### Invalid: reservation not found (expect 404)
DELETE http://localhost:8080/reservations/delete?id=999999

### --- Approve (POST /reservations/approve?id=) ---

###
### Approve reservation (PENDING -> APPROVED)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/approve?id=1

###
### Invalid: missing 'id' param (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/approve

###
### Invalid: reservation not found (expect 404)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/approve?id=999999

###
### Invalid: reservation not PENDING (expect 409, run twice in a row to trigger)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/approve?id=1

### --- Cancel (POST /reservations/cancel?id=) ---

###
### Cancel reservation
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/cancel?id=1

###
### Invalid: missing 'id' param (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/cancel

###
### Invalid: reservation not found (expect 404)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/cancel?id=999999

###
### Invalid: already CANCELLED (expect 409, run twice in a row to trigger)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/cancel?id=1

### --- Validation examples on /create (expect 400 with ErrorResponse body) ---

###
### Invalid: id must be null
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "userId": 11,
  "roomId": 111,
  "startDate": "2026-07-01",
  "endDate": "2026-07-05"
}

###
### Invalid: status must be null
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 11,
  "roomId": 111,
  "startDate": "2026-07-01",
  "endDate": "2026-07-05",
  "status": "APPROVED"
}

###
### Invalid: userId and roomId must not be null
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2026-07-01",
  "endDate": "2026-07-05"
}

###
### Invalid: userId must be >= 0
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": -1,
  "roomId": 111,
  "startDate": "2026-07-01",
  "endDate": "2026-07-05"
}

###
### Invalid: dates must be present or future
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 11,
  "roomId": 111,
  "startDate": "2020-01-01",
  "endDate": "2026-07-05"
}

###
### Invalid: startDate must not be after endDate (business rule, expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 11,
  "roomId": 111,
  "startDate": "2026-07-10",
  "endDate": "2026-07-05"
}

###
### Invalid: overlapping dates for the same room (business rule, expect 409;
### run right after the "Create reservation" request above so room 111 is booked)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 12,
  "roomId": 111,
  "startDate": "2026-07-03",
  "endDate": "2026-07-08"
}

###
### Invalid: malformed JSON body (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/create
Content-Type: application/json

"not valid json"

###
### Invalid: wrong Content-Type (expect 415)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/create
Content-Type: text/plain

{
  "userId": 11,
  "roomId": 111,
  "startDate": "2026-07-01",
  "endDate": "2026-07-05"
}

### --- Availability check (POST /reservation-availability/check) ---

###
### Fixture: book room 500 for 2027-01-10..2027-01-15 (needed by the checks below)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservations/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 80,
  "roomId": 500,
  "startDate": "2027-01-10",
  "endDate": "2027-01-15"
}

###
### Available: room with no reservations at all
POST http://localhost:8080/reservation-availability/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 501,
  "startDate": "2027-01-10",
  "endDate": "2027-01-15"
}

###
### Reserved: overlaps the booked room 500
POST http://localhost:8080/reservation-availability/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 500,
  "startDate": "2027-01-12",
  "endDate": "2027-01-13"
}

###
### Available: same room 500, non-overlapping dates
POST http://localhost:8080/reservation-availability/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 500,
  "startDate": "2027-02-01",
  "endDate": "2027-02-05"
}

###
### Reserved: edge-to-edge overlap (new startDate == existing endDate, boundary is inclusive)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservation-availability/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 500,
  "startDate": "2027-01-15",
  "endDate": "2027-01-20"
}

###
### Invalid: startDate must not be after endDate (business rule, expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservation-availability/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 500,
  "startDate": "2027-01-20",
  "endDate": "2027-01-15"
}

###
### Invalid: startDate must be present or future (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservation-availability/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 500,
  "startDate": "2020-01-01",
  "endDate": "2027-01-13"
}

###
### Invalid: endDate must be present or future (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservation-availability/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 500,
  "startDate": "2027-01-12",
  "endDate": "2020-01-01"
}

###
### Invalid: roomId must not be null (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservation-availability/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2027-01-12",
  "endDate": "2027-01-13"
}

###
### Invalid: roomId must be >= 0 (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservation-availability/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": -1,
  "startDate": "2027-01-12",
  "endDate": "2027-01-13"
}

###
### Invalid: startDate and endDate must not be null (expect 400)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservation-availability/check
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 500
}

###
### Invalid: wrong Content-Type (expect 415)
POST http://localhost:8080/reservation-availability/check
Content-Type: text/plain

{
  "roomId": 500,
  "startDate": "2027-01-12",
  "endDate": "2027-01-13"
}
